item.title: CVE-2022-32244|2024-08-03T07:39:50.380Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20businessobjects%20business%20intelligence%20platform%20%28commentary%20db%29
item.description: Under certain conditions an attacker authenticated as a CMS administrator access the BOE Commentary database and retrieve (non-personal) system data, modify system data but can't make the system unavailable. This needs the attacker to have high privilege access to the same physical/logical network to access information which would otherwise be restricted, leading to low impact on confidentiality and high impact on integrity of the application.
